what is a Longfill?
Spice up your vaping experience with our 10mg Ohm Boy Longfill Booster Kit Nicotine Salts, a perfectly balanced 50VG/50PG blend that comes in a convenient 60ml bottle filled with 20ml of delicious flavor concentrate and VG.

Why should I use a Longfill?
Longfills offer a wide range of nicotine strengths and customizable PG/VG ratios to give consumers more options and flexibility compared to standard variations in the industry. With Ohm Boy Longfill Booster Kit, you can easily create nicotine strengths of 0, 3, 6, 10, 12 & 14mg, and mix in additional boosters for unique flavour and vapour production. This means you can enjoy the flavours on all types of devices.

How do I use a Longfill + booster kits?
Gently twist off the caps of all 4 10ml boosters and the Longfill cap, keeping them to one side. The new nib design for the nicotine shots eliminates the need for manual removal and reduces mess. To use, secure the nib over the longfill nib and make sure the longfill is upright with the 10ml booster facing downwards. Squeeze and release the longfill bottle to let the vacuum do its work, repeating for all 4x 10mls. This method may be slower than pouring or squeezing the 10ml bottles, but it guarantees no mess.
